titles.full: When the Leaves Began to Turn

summaries.short: As the Union’s Holon army nears the Polity’s final stronghold, Chase preps his team for what could be gen:LOCK’s last stand.
summaries.full: While the Polity struggles to hold ground, Chase preps his team for what could be their last stand against the Union’s Nemesii. Later, as an onslaught descends on the streets of Los Angeles, General Marin desperately searches for a way to save humanity, while Holcroft continues to peddle false hope.

summaries.full: In the first episode of un:Locked, hosts Blaine Gibson, Dennise Rodriguez, and Curtis Richardson discuss Season 2, Episode 1 of Gen:Lock "When The Leaves Began To Turn". They recap the exciting return of mech-piloting heroes, theorize where this season will take us, and interview the show's Head Writer- Daniel Dominguez and Voice Actress- Monica Rial, voice of General Marin.
